                {
                    "kind": "text",
                    "text": "An abstract class, defining a drop-down component, with:\nProperties for display styles and classes\nA collection items of type "
                },
                {
                    "kind": "code",
                    "text": "`IgxDropDownItemBaseDirective`"
                },
                {
                    "kind": "text",
                    "text": "\nProperties and methods for navigating (highlighting/focusing) items from the collection\nProperties and methods for selecting items from the collection"
